N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1261.11 - Cleaning and maintenance of aircraft restricted to designated areas

State Regulations

Cleaning of or otherwise maintaining aircraft shall be
accomplished only in areas designated for that purpose by the
manager. Notes
